"{\"uid\": \"allkpop.com-article-2024-07-song-hye-kyo-donates-guidebooks-on-korean-independence-movement-sites-in-paris-ahead-of-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  486    ActressSong Hye-kyoandProfessor Seo Kyung-deokof Sungshin Women's University have teamed up once again for a philanthropic endeavor.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 17th, they announced the donation of guidebooks highlighting Korean independence movement sites in Paris.\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 214, \"end\": 242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_independence_movement\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Korean independence movement\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_independence_movement\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_independence_movement\"}, {\"begin\": 252, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.998751324425594, \"rank\": 0.0012502367144854088, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The guidebooks, produced in both Korean and French, have been distributed in 10,000 copies to the Korean Education Center in France and the Korean Pavilion at the Cit\\u00e9 Internationale Universitaire de Paris.\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 304, \"end\": 310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9008974216806096, \"rank\": 0.10861490392608794, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 358, \"end\": 364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.6318391765114236, \"rank\": 0.5826810827278692, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.or